Downtime happens. We want to be the first to be notified!
Start monitoring in 30 seconds and totally free
Panic Control monitors your webpages and check whether they are up or down. This check uptime is highly configurable.

If your website goes down, don't worry, an email is sent to alert you and your team. You can add multiple contacts to send alerts. we offer you en email alert template, but you can create also your own template!
Downtime in production are irreversible and you want to have a report of your incidents, panic control do that for you, you will be able to view your incidents over a month and over a year
Feel free to send a support request to panic.control.all@gmail.com (from the account e-mail) and we'll be replying soon.
